rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0001
rows.name: Takaka has made another discovery of the century, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Takaka noticed it while watching the Driver scout
below, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Among the Blades that have been resonated with,
there are some that rarely hold an incredible
amount of potential, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Heaven's Holy Grail? The Jewel of Superbia?
Takaka had a feeling they could be even stronger than that, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0005
rows.name:
At a glance, they look like ordinary Blades, but...
Takaka felt that potential intensely, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_04_msg0006
rows.name:
So, if a Driver tries hard, the day should come
when they can meet such a Blade, mo.
